# Higgsfield for RaapTech visuals

When creating, regenerating, or refining marketing imagery for this site
(hero photos, case-study visuals, OG art, short motion clips), prefer the
**Higgsfield MCP** (`higgsfield` server at `https://mcp.higgsfield.ai/mcp`)
over generic image tools.

## Brand constraints for prompts

- Industrial neo-brutalist RaapTech identity — shop floor, sheet metal, MEP,
  Autodesk Fabrication context. Real fabrication atmosphere, not SaaS gloss.
- Palette cues: warm concrete / paper (`#EDE9E0`), black ink (`#0B0B0C`),
  hazard orange (`#FF4D00`). Avoid purple gradients and soft glassmorphism.
- No AI-vendor logos or named AI product branding in the frame.
- Prefer full-bleed, edge-to-edge scenes suitable for hero backgrounds.

## Auth

Higgsfield uses OAuth (no API key). If tools are unavailable or return an
auth error, ask the user to Connect Higgsfield under Cursor Settings → MCP /
Connectors, then retry.
